mim.author: ERAHAIM
mim.name: RmeAI
mim.description: This model contains configuration for the Auto provisioning service.

enumMember.name: SITE_CONFIG_COMPLETE
enumMember.description: Site configuration is completed. The node is ready for integration by OSS.

enumMember.name: OSS_CONFIGURATION_SUCCESSFUL
enumMember.description: The node is successfully configured by OSS.

enumMember.name: INTEGRATION_COMPLETE
enumMember.description: The node is integrated in a network.

enumMember.name: READY_FOR_SERVICE
enumMember.description: Integration is complete. All planned configuration has been applied successfully.

enumMember.name: OSS_CONFIGURATION_FAILED
enumMember.description: Node configuration by OSS has failed.

enumMember.name: ACTIVATING_FEATURES
enumMember.description: All features with valid licenses are activated.

enumMember.name: ACTIVATING_FEATURES_FAILED
enumMember.description: Not all features with valid licenses installed are correctly activated.

enumMember.name: OSS_CONTROL_NODE_CONN
enumMember.description: OSS activates node conection to the control node.

enumMember.name: OSS_CONTROL_NODE_CONN_FAILED
enumMember.description: Node connection to control node failed.

enumMember.name: UNLOCKING_CELLS
enumMember.description: Unlocked cells are coming into service.

enumMember.name: UNLOCKING_CELLS_FAILED
enumMember.description: One or more cells failed to unlock.

enumMember.name: RAN_INTEGRATION_WAS_CANCELLED
enumMember.description: AutoIntegration was cancelled but the ME is still manageable from OSS.

class.name: AutoProvisioning
class.description: This MO class contains configuration items for the Auto provisioning service.

attribute.name: autoProvisioningId
attribute.description: Holds the name used when identifying the MO.

attribute.name: rbsConfigLevel
attribute.description: Show the current stage of auto provisioning for this managed element.
